{"tid":737183,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"DSE等緊放榜未瞓嘅入一入黎!","createTime":"2018-07-10T19:03:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T20:09:59.000Z","uid":194101,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b33401fe31d8b8d04b180bb3f2eac1b18350e3f7","tid":737183,"uid":194101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T19:03:44.000Z","msg":"其實DSE真係唔係斷定你一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入到大學/大專其實都已經無人會care你dse咩成績<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你宜家可以做嘅就係唔好諗咁多!<br />\n或者睇下世界盃令自己分下心 <br />\n唔好太緊張<br />\n*如果已經知道一定入asso/hd 而且無用eapp報定嘅同學仔<br />\n我建議你準備好:<br />\n1.現金 ~$800 (飛的同留位費用嘅 熱門asso課程都好快滿)<br />\n2.身份證副本<br />\n3.學生證副本<br />\n4.成績表<br />\n同埋同學收到成績之後要開始重新排jupas <br />\n用過來人身份 <br />\n排jupas其實都係一門學問<br />\n話說我之前都開咗個excel 綜合曬所有資料先報jupas<br />\n千祈唔好睇小!!<br />\n祝大家聽日都有理想成績<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 2017考生"},{"pid":"c0a60ec1e07f8d4346334f3a46e643f7d7ebcca9","tid":737183,"uid":194101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T19:18:15.000Z","msg":"你地有咩問題都可以問!識問一定答!"},{"pid":"5c3e2d66ed2621067a8b52f1f1b5d67bcf40b521","tid":737183,"uid":194101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T19:53:36.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"ed3473de14ccac5078c4b5b9509f8c7b05f8c558","tid":737183,"uid":174069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T19:59:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a3c9d62e7229ad8b963580262d37e205612ac3a","tid":737183,"uid":194101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed3473de14ccac5078c4b5b9509f8c7b05f8c558","tid":737183,"uid":174069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T19:59:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T20:02:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" c